Kenneth MacDonald (American actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kenneth_MacDonald_(American_actor) 0 Kenneth MacDonald (born Kenneth Dollins, September 8, 1901 – May 5, 1972) was an American film actor. Born in Portland, Indiana, MacDonald made more than 220 film and television appearances between 1931 and 1970. His name is sometimes seen as Kenneth McDonald.
